>>__ Parse.temp_set_grammars $ valOf $ grammarDB {thyname="hol"};
## `WORD_CONV`

``` hol4
wordsLib.WORD_CONV : conv
```

------------------------------------------------------------------------

Conversion for words.

The conversion `WORD_CONV` applies the simpset fragment `WORD_ss`.

### Example

``` hol4
>>__ load "wordsLib";

>>+ wordsLib.WORD_CONV “c * (a + b) !! (b + a) * c”
```

